  <brief_title>Extension Study of the Safety and Efficacy of Enteric-coated Mycophenolate Sodium in Kidney Transplant Recipients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Open-label, Multicenter, International Follow-up Study on the Safety and Efficacy of Enteric-coated Mycophenolate Sodium (EC-MPS) in Kidney Transplant Recipients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
