  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this extension study is to allow patients being treated with enteric-coated
      mycophenolate sodium (core study CERL080A2405LA01) to continue on the same treatment and to
      assess the long-term safety of EC-MPS.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
